# 10. Pricing & Additional Fees

## 10.1 Shipping Price Calculation

-   Each good is priced by weight (kg) OR area (m²)

-   The higher calculated value is used

-   Default prices loaded from goods type catalog

-   Customer-specific stored discounts applied automatically

## 10.2 Additional Fees

The system supports adding extra charges to customer invoices:

-   Port of Beirut fees (if applicable)

-   Internal transport/delivery charges

-   Customs handling fees

-   Other miscellaneous charges

## 10.3 Pricing Overrides

-   Staff may override per-kg price, per-m² price, or final total

-   All overrides require reason and are fully audited

-   Override history preserved for dispute resolution

