## 17.1 WhatsApp Business API Integration

Automated customer notifications via the Official WhatsApp Business API (Meta Cloud API) at key workflow stages. This provides production-grade, reliable messaging with 99.9% delivery guarantee.

**API Specifications:**

-   Provider: Meta Cloud API (recommended) or Twilio (alternative)

-   Cost: Approximately $0.05–$0.08 per message (varies by country)

-   Reliability: 99.9% guaranteed delivery

-   Risk: None (legitimate, officially supported business use)

**Pre-Approved Message Templates:**

-   Price List Notification – Sent upon customer registration

-   Goods Received Notification – Confirmation with package reference and weight

-   Documents for Signature – Request for responsibility declaration and drug-free certification

-   Shipment Status Update – Container, vessel, status, and ETA information

-   Arrival Notification – Pickup location and arrival confirmation

-   Invoice Ready – Invoice delivery with total amount

**Technical Implementation:**

-   Full media support (photos, documents, invoices)

-   Webhook integration for delivery status tracking (sent, delivered, read, failed)

-   Bilingual template support (English and Arabic)

-   Complete message logging and audit trail

**Setup Requirements:**

-   Meta Business Account creation and verification (1–3 days)

-   Phone number registration for sending notifications

-   Message template approval by Meta (24–48 hours)

**Estimated Monthly Cost:** 100 customers × 5 notifications = 500 messages × $0.05 = approximately $25/month

